---
import { Image, Picture } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../../layouts/layout.astro";
import Container from "../../components/page-container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "../../components/section-head.astro";
import Link from "./../../components/elements/link.astro";
import bcnPlane from "../../assets/bcn-from-plane.jpg";
---

<Layout title={"Barcelona English Speakers Community"}>
  <Container class:list={"!max-w-5xl"}>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Barcelona English Speakers</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        <strong>Barcelona English Speakers</strong> is a thriving Whatsapp
        community group run by English-speaking people living in Barcelona.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <main class="mt-8 lg:mt-16">
      <div class="my-4 lg:my-8 mx-auto max-w-6xl rounded-lg">
        <Picture
          src={bcnPlane}
          format="avif"
          widths={[1024, 800]}
          alt="Barcelona from the plane"
          quality={"mid"}
          class:list={"w-full"}
        />

        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight text-center my-8 lg:my-16 prose !max-w-none"
        >
          About the community
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl prose my-8">
          The group started in 2018 to offer personal experiences, tips, support
          and general help to other English speaking people who had just moved
          to Barcelona. Since the summer of 2023, the group has welcomed over
          500 members and counting!
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl prose my-8">
          We host monthly meet-ups, where we attract around 20-30 people and we
          also have an active events channel on our Whatsapp group, where people
          can propose other events such as getting together for a beer.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl prose my-8">
          Since the start of 2023 the core admin group has attracted the
          collaboration from other foreigners living and working in Barcelona,
          of which there are about 10 seasoned experts and together we share
          1000â€™s of hours of experience. We love to share this experience with
          the wider group and with each other and we author a set of up-to-date
          blog posts, guides and articles, which help newcomers navigate their
          way through life in Barcelona! Checkout our <a href="/blog">Blog</a>.
        </p>

        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-5xl tracking-tight text-center my-8 lg:my-16 prose !max-w-none"
        >
          Join the community
        </h2>

        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl prose my-8">
          To join our Barcelona chat group, hit the button below!
        </p>

        <div class="flex mt-4 justify-center">
          <Link
            href="https://chat.whatsapp.com/FZMPjvsMwFzBwUBpjauCoa"
            style="primary"
            target="_blank"
          >
            Join (Whatsapp Group)
          </Link>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </Container>
</Layout>
